{"tid":2359013,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"各方打氣","createTime":"2021-01-08T14:13:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T14:13:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7fc67ca3a15f112eb5a19c8579a64df463eb1a8d","tid":2359013,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T14:13:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210108/BUYFVQU4TBA37D4TMAVV7G7AVQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210108%2FBUYFVQU4TBA37D4TMAVV7G7AVQ%2F&d=M%2BQ4vsyFJ%2Bls%2BsYkNkBEXdVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=1b15fbfc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210108%2FBUYFVQU4TBA37D4TMAVV7G7AVQ%2F&h=efda0b0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210108/BUYFVQU4TBA37D4TMAVV7G7AVQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n各方打氣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/iY8X5vj3KiPhUgAvadNMaIufVGk=/3280x3169/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/P3O4PDFIV5ASLCBNCMITMR7SBM.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FiY8X5vj3KiPhUgAvadNMaIufVGk%3D%2F3280x3169%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FP3O4PDFIV5ASLCBNCMITMR7SBM.JPG&h=984e02f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒創辦人黎智英被控欺詐及勾結外國勢力，除夕夜起再被無理還柙後，53名民主派人士前日亦被警方國安處指控涉顛覆國家政權。署名「掛念你的手足」的讀者來函，慨嘆大搜捕令市民非常難過，但靜下來就會想起黎的無畏無懼。他斥責極權橫蠻，認為港人絕對不能讓極權暴政得逞，寄語黎智英「大家都撐住呀！」<br />\n<br />\n大搜捕儼如港版台灣美麗島事件，一封來自台灣的親筆信此時送抵蘋果大樓，既說給黎智英聽，也告訴港人，「香港之所以美麗，就是因為住了有良知的香港人」。"}]}